rows.label: tlk42300042_01_msg0001
rows.name: Friends seen red barrels around town?

rows.label: tlk42300042_01_msg0002
rows.name:
Those handled by Nopon trade guild.
They marked with red paint so they
easy to keep track of.

rows.label: tlk42300042_01_msg0003
rows.name:
Actually not just Avaritia Trade
Guild that use them. They have
nationwide application.

rows.label: tlk42300042_01_msg0004
rows.name:
Sometimes we try to make sure they
under lock and key.

rows.label: tlk42300042_01_msg0005
rows.name:
But vandalism of barrels on rise lately.
Is getting a bit worrying...
